com.seamless.ers.interfaces.external.data
Class Principal

java.lang.Object
  com.seamless.ers.interfaces.external.data.Principal

public class Principal
extends java.lang.Object

A principal is an entity in the ERS, and is either a reseller or a subscriber. A principal is identified by a principalId.
